acacia_log.buy:
#@ keep
#@ impulse
#@ manual
execute at @p[distance=..3] if score @p[distance=0] Wallet < acacia_log_buy_16 Price run tellraw @p[distance=0] [{"text":"Not enough money. Your balance is $","color":"red"},{"score":{"name":"*","objective":"Wallet"}}]
execute at @p[distance=..3] unless entity @a[scores={Transaction=3}] if score @p[distance=0] Wallet >= acacia_log_buy_16 Price run scoreboard players set @p[distance=0,scores={Transaction=0}] Transaction 3
#@ conditional
scoreboard players operation @p[scores={Transaction=3}] Wallet -= acacia_log_buy_16 Price

give @p[scores={Transaction=3}] acacia_log 16
#@ conditional
tellraw @p[scores={Transaction=3}] [{"text":"Your new balance is $","color":"yellow"},{"score":{"name":"*","objective":"Wallet"}}]
scoreboard players set @p[scores={Transaction=3}] Transaction 0
